These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, plum
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating plum and the person who's sport is swimming have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | plum | strawberry  |
| Sport   | swimming    | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, broccoli
1. the person drinking lemonade and the person eating eggplant have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk      | lemonade       |
| Food       | broccoli | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, reggae
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, skiing
1. the fan d&b and the person who's sport is parkour have different parity positions##9
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | d&b       |
| Sport         | parkour | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, malaysian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the malaysian and the person who's sport is basketball have different parity positions##9
3. the italian is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian |
| Sport         | tennis | basketball  |

 #################################

 
