.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-6::.
There 2 different types of food: tomato, lettuce
2 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit
1. the owner of the frog and the person eating lettuce have the same parity positions##9
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2    |
| Food   | lettuce | tomato  |
| Pet    | frog       | rabbit |

